  <brief_title>Assessment of Renal Function in Cirrhotic Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Assessment of Renal Function in Cirrhotic Patients -A Comparison of Cystatin C and Creatinine Based Calculations to 125I-iothalamate</official_title>
  <sponsors>
